<br>
I am considering replacing the RBB with a CoCW... although I will not be able to also afford a Rubicite Girdle to pair it with (any 'cheap' waist recommendations?). <br>
<br>
I just wanted to confirm with you elders whether the add'l haste would more than compensate the loss in Hps and Sta.<br>
<br>
FYI I'm level 60, usually at around 1290ac 4600hps with Aegolism and (non uber) ranger and shaman buffs on.<br>
